---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us"
  description="Learn about Student Utility Hub, a privacy-first collection of calculators and academic planning tools for college students in India."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <span class="rounded-full border border-hairline bg-canvas px-3 py-1 font-mono text-xs font-semibold text-mute">
      About the Project
    </span>
    <h1 class="mt-4 font-sans text-3xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.96px] text-ink sm:text-4xl">
      About Student Utility Hub.
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-mute font-mono">
      Distraction-free calculations for academic success.
    </p>

    <!-- Content Sections -->
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-body">
      <section class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">
          Why we exist
        </h2>
        <p>
          Indian college students are subject to demanding regulations—most notably the mandatory 75% attendance rule and complex multi-tier SGPA/CGPA conversions. Unfortunately, most websites that offer academic calculators are slow, cluttered with intrusive popups, and track user data.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Student Utility Hub</strong> was built as an antidote. We provide a premium, clean, developer-style interface that does calculations instantly in your browser, works perfectly on mobile phones, and respects your privacy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="h-px bg-hairline"></div>

      <section class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">
          Privacy-First Architecture
        </h2>
        <p>
          We believe your academic data belongs to you. Student Utility Hub operates on a <strong>client-side local-first architecture</strong>:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside flex flex-col gap-2 pl-2">
          <li><strong>No Databases:</strong> We do not store your grades, subjects, or attendance records on remote servers.</li>
          <li><strong>LocalStorage Cache:</strong> All subjects, credit configurations, and percentages are saved in your browser's local cache. Clearing your browser data deletes them.</li>
          <li><strong>Zero Tracking:</strong> We run no hidden tracking pixels. The website is statically generated and deployed on the edge for high security.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="h-px bg-hairline"></div>

      <section class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">
          Our Technology Stack
        </h2>
        <p>
          To deliver a modern web experience, the platform is built on:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside flex flex-col gap-2 pl-2">
          <li><strong class="text-ink">Astro MPA:</strong> A multi-page framework that renders clean, zero-JS HTML by default, ensuring instant loads and flawless SEO.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-ink">Tailwind CSS v4:</strong> Utilizing a CSS-first design system with curated variables for stark theme configurations.</li>
          <li><strong class="text-ink">Cloudflare Pages:</strong> Hosted directly at the network edge for robust global delivery and uptime.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
